    <h3>What is RemindMail?</h3>
    <p><strong>RemindMail</strong> is a reminder online service whose aim is to help you to be more efficient and productive by reducing amount of stored &quot;follow-up&quot; or unread&nbsp;e-mails in your personal mailbox. Or, simply when you need to make a reminder and forget about the case until you need it - RemindMail will send it back to you&nbsp;on time!</p>
    <p>RemindMail is unique and universal - you can create reminders even without being registered, just send an e-mail to service and you will get it back at a scheduled time which you decide and set yourself.&nbsp;This service is not linked to any mailing providers or reminder&nbsp;services, you can use it with your private or work e-mail address. By registering you will get more - access to all scheduled and past reminders you created&nbsp;with possibility to read and edit them. Through website&nbsp;facilities you&nbsp;will also have a possibility to create reminders using comprehensive e-mail redactor.</p>
